abstract: Footage shows the rollout ceremonies for Endeavour, including the display of colors, invocation, and speeches by Sam Iacobellis, Executive Vice-President and CEO of Rockwell International, Richard H. Truly, Administrator for NASA, and Senator Jake Garn (Utah). The tape ends during the speech by Senator Garn and continues on part two (Input Processing ID 2000152220, Document ID 20010010951). Endeavour rolls out to music provided by the band on-site.
title: Rollout of Endeavour at Palmdale, California (Part 1 of 2)
